quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  76,1,Did (it) come on the human/mankind (a) period of time from the long time he was not a mentioned/remembered thing
  76,2,"That We, We created the human/mankind from a drop/male`s or female`s secretion mixtures (of secretions), We test him, so We made/created him hearing/listening, seeing/knowing"
  76,3,"That We, We guided him the way/path , either (he is) thankful/grateful and either (an insistent) disbeliever"
  76,4,"That We prepared/made ready for the disbelievers chains/successions, and leather or iron collars or handcuffs and blazing/inflaming (punishment)"
  76,5,That truly the righteous/charitable drink from a cup its mixture/blend was camphor
  76,6,"A water well/spring God`s worshippers/slaves drink by it, they cause it to flow bursting/flowing"
  76,7,"They fulfill/complete with the vow/duty (on oneself) , and they fear a day/time its evil/harm was spread and scattered"
  76,8,"And they feed the food on (inspite of) its love/like (to it to) a poorest of poor/poor oppressed and an orphan ,and a captive/prisoner"
  76,9,"(They say): \"Truly we feed you for God`s sake , we do not want from you a reward/reimbursement ,and nor thankfulness/gratefulness"
  76,10,"We (E), fear from our Lord a severe (gloomy) difficult/evil day/time"
  76,11,"So God protected/preserved them (from) that the day`s/time`s bad/evil/harm, and He made them meet/find beauty and goodness and delight/happiness"
  76,12,And He rewarded/reimbursed them because (of) what they were patient (by) treed gardens/paradises and silk
  76,13,"Resting/reclining in it on the luxurious beds/couches, they do not see in it sun and nor severe cold/anger"
  76,14,"And its shades/shadows (are) near on them, and its fruit harvests was manipulated/dangled low dangling/manipulating"
  76,15,And (they are) being circled around on them with drinking cups from silver and cups (that) were/are clear glass/mirrors
  76,16,"Clear glass/mirrors from silver, they predestined/evaluated it predestination/evaluation"
  76,17,And they be given drink in it (in) a cup its mixture/blend was ginger/wine
  76,18,"A water spring/well in it, it is named Salsbeelan/fresh, smooth and pleasant water fountain"
  76,19,"And immortal/eternal children/new borns circle/walk around them, if you saw/understood them you thought/supposed them (that) they (are) scattered/sprinkled pearls"
  76,20,"And if you saw/understood, then you saw/understood comfort and ease/blessing and a great ownership/kingdom"
  76,21,"Their tops (covers them) clothes/garments (from) green sarcenet (certain type of silk or brocade) and brocade (silk and gold fabric), and they were bejeweled/ornamented (with) bracelets from silver, and their Lord gave/made them drink a pure/clear drink"
  76,22,"That truly that was for you a reward/reimbursement , and your striving/endeavor was/is thanked"